Gloria closes by saying; “separate your personal life from the business and all else will work out.” The pilot project is being shut down due to lack of commercial viability. Ministry of Lands restores ownership of part of the Vipingo Industrial Park land after it emerged that there was double registration of title deed. Medics say the only proven means of controlling spread of the virus is wearing masks and screening of patients. Second psychiatric report to be produced on March 12 before court gives directions in the Sh14 million corruption case. The cumulative recoveries in the country now stand at 87,099.